  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat a grill or grill pan to medium-high heat.",
    "2. Grill the pork belly for 5-7 minutes per side, or until it reaches an internal temperature of 145°F (63°C).",
    "3. Let the pork rest for 5 minutes before slicing.",
    "4. Toast the ciabatta bread until crispy.",
    "5. Spread a layer of herb mayonnaise on each slice of bread.",
    "6. Add sliced pork, pickled carrots, cucumber, cilantro, and chili sauce (if using) on top of the mayonnaise.",
    "7. Top with shredded lettuce.",
    "8. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
